# Shell

This environment uses **PowerShell** on Windows. Never use bash syntax.

## Forbidden

- `&&` and `||` to chain commands — run commands separately instead
- Heredoc `<<'EOF'` — pass strings directly with `-m "message"`
- `$(...)` subshells
- Bash-specific redirections (`2>/dev/null || true`)

## Instead

- Run commands **one at a time** in separate shell calls
- Use PowerShell-compatible flags and quoting
